results.name: Least number m to appear exactly n times in A095972.
comment: One has n/2 <= A095972(n)+1 <= n, therefore an integer m can appear in A095972 only between indices m and 2m, and this sequence is effectively computable.
results.author: _M. F. Hasler_, Nov 03 2012
